trans-unit.source: This section contains the help topics for the **ISE** module, which includes commands that you can use in Windows PowerShell Integrated Scripting Environment (ISE).
trans-unit.target: 本部分包含有关 **ISE** 模块的帮助主题，此模块包含可在 Windows PowerShell 集成脚本环境 (ISE) 中使用的命令。

trans-unit.source: The **ISE** module is installed with Windows PowerShell.
trans-unit.target: **ISE** 模块随 Windows PowerShell 一起安装。
